  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Otsutsuki.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The Ōtsutsuki travel through dimensions and space, which requires they have the body to do so. At 1st level, you do not need to breathe, you can remain awake for 72 hours before any negative effects that come with not resting affect you, and when you take a long rest, you do not sleep. Instead, you meditate for 4 hours while being aware of what happens around you as if fully awake.</p><p data-start=\"388\" data-end=\"668\">At 7th level, your ability to hover manifests more prominently. As a bonus action, you can gain a flying speed of 30 ft. Flying this way uses up one concentration slot, but you cannot lose concentration on this ability. At 15th level, flying no longer uses a concentration slot.</p><p data-start=\"670\" data-end=\"934\" data-is-last-node data-is-only-node>At 11th level, your body adapts to greater pressure. Whenever you would take damage, except for psychic, you can reduce the damage by an amount equal to 3× your Constitution modifier. You can do this a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus per long rest</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
